summary:
The most important thing when learning a new framework, especially ones which have a new way of doing things is to understand how to think (or design) solutions to a problem.
Next.js claims the major issue it fixes on top of React.js is &ldquo;Pre Rendering&rdquo;
What is Pre Rendering Historically frameworks like JSP used to render the HTML content of the page on the server-side and send the rendered HTML page to the browser.
